Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,429,0000,0000,0000,,Stage 3
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,429,0000,0000,0000,,The Lying Classmate.


Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:05.94,Default,1,0000,0000,0000,,Imperial calendar. August 10th, 2010.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.78,0:00:11.05,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,The New Britannian Empire declared war on Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:18.84,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,Japan, which was unable to mount any resistance against Britannia's newest weapon, the Knightmare Frame,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:25.59,Default,4,0000,0000,0000,,was defeated, and had it's freedom... rights... honor... and name taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:32.80,Default,5,0000,0000,0000,,11. That was the new name for the Japanese people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:12.44,Default,7,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:15.04,Default,7,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:18.11,Default,8,0000,0000,0000,,Giving me this strange power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:37.77,Default,9,0000,0000,0000,,Why? The special troops were....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:43.47,Default,10,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.97,Default,11,0000,0000,0000,,What is a Britannian student doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:46.97,Default,12,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:48.13,Default,13,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:52.37,Default,14,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:54.39,Default,15,0000,0000,0000,,Get down from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:55.86,Default,16,0000,0000,0000,,Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:02:59.74,Default,17,0000,0000,0000,,You... what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:04.41,Default,18,0000,0000,0000,,I see. She needs to see this power firsthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:07.23,Default,19,0000,0000,0000,,I am Alan Spacer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:08.41,Default,20,0000,0000,0000,,My father is a duke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:09.76,Default,21,0000,0000,0000,,A duke...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:12.61,Default,22,0000,0000,0000,,I have an ID card in back pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:15.28,Default,23,0000,0000,0000,,After you check it, I would like to request protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.11,Default,24,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your hands up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:25.45,Default,25,0000,0000,0000,,I will take the ID out myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:28.43,Default,26,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me... your Knightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:38.76,Default,27,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:40.77,Default,28,0000,0000,0000,,The password is XG2.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:42.03,Default,29,0000,0000,0000,,The ID is 2D4.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:44.88,Default,30,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:52.05,Default,31,0000,0000,0000,,What... did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.80,Default,32,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:00.80,Default,33,0000,0000,0000,,You missed your chance to get to heaven, Soldier Kurugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:02.05,Default,34,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:03.78,Default,35,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.18,Default,36,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we're still in the Shinjuku Ghetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:11.52,Default,37,0000,0000,0000,,You're near Prince Clovis, so we're in a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:14.40,Default,38,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku-kun, this protected you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:18.20,Default,39,0000,0000,0000,,The shell damaged the outside though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.69,Default,40,0000,0000,0000,,A keepsake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:20.97,Default,41,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:25.58,Default,42,0000,0000,0000,,There is a belief in these parts that such keepsakes contain spirits that protect their owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:26.48,Default,43,0000,0000,0000,,Are these...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:26.87,Default,44,0000,0000,0000,,Um is Lelou...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:30.40,Default,45,0000,0000,0000,,What's the current situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.82,Default,46,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that the poison gas been released.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:35.19,Default,47,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that there were a large amount of casualties among the 11's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:37.83,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that the culprit has not been found yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:39.49,Default,49,0000,0000,0000,,I see... not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:44.02,Default,50,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier Kururugi, what sort of experience do you have piloting the Knightmare Frame?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:44.46,Default,51,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:45.79,Default,52,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:47.93,Default,53,0000,0000,0000,,A person who is an 11 cannot become a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:50.09,Default,54,0000,0000,0000,,And if you could?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.21,Default,55,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:55.54,Default,56,0000,0000,0000,,A one-of-a-kind Knightmare awaits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:56.80,Default,57,0000,0000,0000,,Riding it will change you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:59.23,Default,58,0000,0000,0000,,Both you and your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:01.86,Default,59,0000,0000,0000,,Your dreams will be reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:10.57,Default,60,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you Britannia... how dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:12.75,Default,61,0000,0000,0000,,Kallen! Don't move yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.32,Default,62,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:17.42,Default,63,0000,0000,0000,,I'll act as a decoy so, Ougi-san, you guys get everyone out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.74,Default,64,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones left fighting shall be the resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:20.63,Default,65,0000,0000,0000,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.75,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,But if we're surrounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:27.60,Default,67 (TV),0000,0000,0000,,And at this time, this chip...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:30.75,Default,68,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, I got fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:31.87,Default,69,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you keep snacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:32.72,Default,70,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:38.73,Default,71,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.14,Default,72,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you calling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:41.25,Default,73,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.20,Default,74,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep ditching you'll be held back a grade...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.29,Default,75,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a TV there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:45.57,Default,76,0000,0000,0000,,TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.86,Default,77,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. It's kind of important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.83,Default,78,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:52.48,Default,79,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, can I borrow this for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.11,Default,80,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:54.26,Default,81,0000,0000,0000,,The news.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:55.85,Default,82,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything on Shinjuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:57.00,Default,83,0000,0000,0000,,The news...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:06:00.29,Default,84,0000,0000,0000,,Um... there're just some traffic jams, but nothing other than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:01.92,Default,85,0000,0000,0000,,And the reason for those traffic jams?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:02.91,Default,86,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:04.20,Default,87,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really say here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:09.28,Default,88,0000,0000,0000,,I see... so they plan on having the army make an announcement after everything is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:14.37,Default,89,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... you're doing some weird type of gambling again, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.49,Default,90,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before that it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:17.76,Default,91,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:22.40,Default,92,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and tell my little sister that I'll be getting home late, okay? Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:24.55,Default,94,0000,0000,0000,,Aw jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:26.35,Default,95,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he always so self-centered?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:31.32,Default,96,0000,0000,0000,,The number that you have called is currently...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:31.32,Default,97,0000,0000,0000,,This again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:34.72,Default,98,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the situation is hidden from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:36.44,Default,99,0000,0000,0000,,it's difficult to determine the reinforcements that you must send.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:39.00,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, these are all the pieces for the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:43.20,Default,101,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, getting through this many enemies by myself will be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:45.70,Default,102,0000,0000,0000,,It is also dangerous to approximate things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:53.22,Default,103,0000,0000,0000,,How about you pay me back for getting me involved in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.53,Default,104,0000,0000,0000,,That Glasgow huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:05.81,Default,105,0000,0000,0000,,30 more minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:07.26,Default,106,0000,0000,0000,,The west exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:07.94,Default,107,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:10.28,Default,108,0000,0000,0000,,Use the railroad and move towards the west exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:10.73,Default,109,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:12.49,Default,110,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know this code?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:14.03,Default,111,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:15.78,Default,112,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to win, believe in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:16.70,Default,113,0000,0000,0000,,Win...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.88,Default,114,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:27.75,Default,115,0000,0000,0000,,What a cowardly 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:30.84,Default,116,0000,0000,0000,,If all you can do is run, there's no fun in hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:36.41,Default,117,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for believing me, I will let you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:37.90,Default,118,0000,0000,0000,,Jump up onto this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:38.64,Default,119,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:43.47,Default,120,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think that this would work?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:45.65,Default,121,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... a plan like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.32,Default,122,0000,0000,0000,,You, chase the Glasgow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.40,Default,123,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:50.06,Default,124,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.31,Default,125,0000,0000,0000,,A-Attacking their own side?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.12,Default,126,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard, what platoon are you from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.54,Default,127,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy has only one arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:01.01,Default,128,0000,0000,0000,,No way... the terrorists...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:06.70,Default,129,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:19.89,Default,130,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:22.13,Default,131,0000,0000,0000,,But... how did you get the Sutherland...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.51,Default,132,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.99,Default,133,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Kallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.64,Default,134,0000,0000,0000,,What was that transmission just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:30.42,Default,135,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ougi-san, you guys heard it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:30.89,Default,136,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.89,Default,137,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshitaka and the rest will be here soon as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.45,Default,138,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:36.66,Default,139,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:40.04,Default,140,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you the things that are inside of that train there as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.58,Default,141,0000,0000,0000,,They're some tools that you can use in order to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:45.25,Default,142,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to use these and win, enter in under my command!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:49.90,Default,143,0000,0000,0000,,There're some over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:50.88,Default,144,0000,0000,0000,,Over here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.49,Default,145,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:54.07,Default,146,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should listen to him for a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:56.31,Default,147,0000,0000,0000,,This many... how did he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:57.90,Default,148,0000,0000,0000,,You there in the Glasgow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:08:58.91,Default,149,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:08:59.96,Default,150,0000,0000,0000,,You stay in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:02.49,Default,151,0000,0000,0000,,That machine is geared towards disturbance tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:03.29,Default,152,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:05.06,Default,153,0000,0000,0000,,How is your energy filler?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:06.45,Default,154,0000,0000,0000,,About 15 minutes left...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:08.10,Default,155,0000,0000,0000,,Then, get a new pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:10.82,Default,156,0000,0000,0000,,In 10 minutes I'll send you some new orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.83,Default,157,0000,0000,0000,,Phew, this is more tiring than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:18.72,Default,158,0000,0000,0000,,But, I must remain steadfast to see this through to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:22.10,Default,159,0000,0000,0000,,The stakes of this game are peoples' lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:30.96,Default,160,0000,0000,0000,,The terrorists in 11 are putting up some resistance but it's hardly a threat to our force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:32.29,Default,162,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:33.23,Default,163,0000,0000,0000,,And more importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:34.81,Default,164,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:35.99,Default,165,0000,0000,0000,,The gas capsule is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.42,Default,166,0000,0000,0000,,Under control, I hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.08,Default,167,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:39.50,Default,168,0000,0000,0000,,The girl can still be taken back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:42.68,Default,169,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, without taking her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.61,Default,170,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:48.58,Default,171,0000,0000,0000,,The IFF outnumbers us, and we know nothing of its tactics!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:51.75,Default,172,0000,0000,0000,,They're completely confident in their numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.01,Default,173,0000,0000,0000,,They have no need for traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.37,Default,174,0000,0000,0000,,You guys just go to the points as instructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:56.52,Default,175,0000,0000,0000,,D-1, can you move it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:58.95,Default,176,0000,0000,0000,,The controls should basically be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:00.93,Default,177,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:02.39,Default,178,0000,0000,0000,,At least give me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.09,Default,179,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:05.15,Default,180,0000,0000,0000,,What if the transmission is being monitored?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:09.97,Default,181,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, if Q-1 is on time, then in 23 seconds the enemy Sutherlands will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:10.99,Default,182,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely to your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:12.67,Default,183,0000,0000,0000,,Just fire into the line there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:14.65,Default,184,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, what does he think he's sayin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:17.45,Default,185,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, check your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:19.11,Default,186,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:22.55,Default,187,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy troop at point F-3-1!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:23.97,Default,188,0000,0000,0000,,A diversion huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:24.98,Default,189,0000,0000,0000,,How futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:27.31,Default,190,0000,0000,0000,,The Lazerus troop should proceed as normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:29.04,Default,191,0000,0000,0000,,We will make Orion and Valerie go to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:30.15,Default,192,0000,0000,0000,,We will strike them from the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:34.83,Default,193,0000,0000,0000,,3... 2... 1... Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:37.92,Default,194,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.85,Default,195,0000,0000,0000,,Group Orion and Group Valerie: communications lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.08,Default,196,0000,0000,0000,,An ambush?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.75,Default,197,0000,0000,0000,,The ID signal is a double-edged sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:57.51,Default,198,0000,0000,0000,,And if the terrorists follow my commands, we've already won.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:00.20,Default,199,0000,0000,0000,,P-1, P-4, P-7.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:03.44,Default,200,0000,0000,0000,,Move 100 meters to the right and turn the Slash Hawk to the 3-O'clock direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:05.63,Default,201,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Listen to this voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:07.93,Default,202,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. Guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.23,Default,203,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready yet P-5?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.36,Default,204,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me weird names!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:14.67,Default,205,0000,0000,0000,,In the front, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:18.56,Default,206,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy has moved to D-2-A!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:21.04,Default,207,0000,0000,0000,,Lazerus troops... No! Groube pick up the slack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:24.70,Default,208,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Our mech army is being outmaneuvered by terrorists...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.04,Default,209,0000,0000,0000,,Groube has ejected!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:35.08,Default,210,0000,0000,0000,,The vehicle is lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:36.20,Default,211,0000,0000,0000,,Change the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.79,Default,212,0000,0000,0000,,Our transmissions are being monitored!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:38.78,Default,213,0000,0000,0000,,We have done it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:39.54,Default,214,0000,0000,0000,,Four times in fact!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:40.45,Default,215,0000,0000,0000,,Do it one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:42.22,Default,216,0000,0000,0000,,What a disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:44.05,Default,217,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.11,Default,218,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:45.94,Default,219,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:47.18,Default,220,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the middle of a strategy meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.91,Default,221,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I was thinking of making the new troop available...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:51.80,Default,222,0000,0000,0000,,Now is not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:54.90,Default,223,0000,0000,0000,,R-2, launch anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:57.73,Default,224,0000,0000,0000,,B-7, a UN Round.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:01.32,Default,225,0000,0000,0000,,Group N, move forward as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:04.91,Default,226,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you 11's!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:08.09,Default,227,0000,0000,0000,,Lazerus troops' signals have disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.01,Default,228,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:10.91,Default,229,0000,0000,0000,,Put up Quincy's group!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.77,Default,230,0000,0000,0000,,But, Your Majesty, if we do that, the formation...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:16.68,Default,231,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the enemy has five choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:20.00,Default,232,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry about breaking formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:22.58,Default,233,0000,0000,0000,,We'll certainly catch the enemy's troops here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.10,Default,234,0000,0000,0000,,Are they going to break formation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.80,Default,235,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? They've taken the worst possible approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:34.34,Default,236,0000,0000,0000,,Q-1, the map is accurate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:36.30,Default,237,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the old town is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:38.14,Default,238,0000,0000,0000,,But without looking at the actual scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:38.90,Default,239,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:41.48,Default,240,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Send Lerus in too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:43.17,Default,241,0000,0000,0000,,Mission number 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.26,Default,242,0000,0000,0000,,Enclose them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.31,Default,243,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrate your firepower!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:46.74,Default,244,0000,0000,0000,,Are the preparations complete?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:49.65,Default,245,0000,0000,0000,,The terrorists main strength is in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.36,Default,246,0000,0000,0000,,Crush them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:58.08,Default,247,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:58.93,Default,248,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy isn't there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.43,Default,249,0000,0000,0000,,This is Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:21.62,Default,250,0000,0000,0000,,It IS possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.86,Default,251,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it. I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:25.53,Default,252,0000,0000,0000,,Britannia can be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:28.67,Default,253,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.45,Default,254,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I fighting against?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:34.64,Default,255,0000,0000,0000,,This guy could be better than Toudou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:36.00,Default,256,0000,0000,0000,,Lloyd!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.37,Default,257,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.03,Default,258,0000,0000,0000,,Could you win, if we used your toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:44.46,Default,259,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty. Please call it the Lancelot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:51.20,Default,260,0000,0000,0000,,Cooperative Weapon 301.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:52.62,Default,261,0000,0000,0000,,Activating Lancelot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:53.99,Default,262,0000,0000,0000,,Activating Lancelot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:55.65,Default,263,0000,0000,0000,,Hatch is free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:58.56,Default,264,0000,0000,0000,,301, Lancelot, standby for activation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.52,Default,265,0000,0000,0000,,Beginning engine rotation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.53,Default,266,0000,0000,0000,,What about the manual?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:03.52,Default,267,0000,0000,0000,,Has it been put to practical use?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:04.63,Default,268,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:07.62,Default,269,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was a simulator, you still are top class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:10.44,Default,270,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that you just told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:12.11,Default,271,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:15.04,Default,271,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible, but the chances are close to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:17.45,Default,272,0000,0000,0000,,But they're not zero, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:23.03,Default,273,0000,0000,0000,,That's true... but I don't want you to do anything over the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:25.79,Default,275,0000,0000,0000,,It's a new system so there's no ejection system implemented yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:28.28,Default,276,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I understand, Cecile-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:32.28,Default,277,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:38.49,Default,278,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... the Special Dispatch Cooperative Technology Department's secret cooperative weapon, the Lancelot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:42.39,Default,279,0000,0000,0000,,It's the only 7th generation Knightmare Frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:46.36,Default,280,0000,0000,0000,,Well then Suzaku-kun. How about we begin deployment soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:48.96,Default,281,0000,0000,0000,,Beginning deployment. Begin from phase 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.37,Default,282,0000,0000,0000,,Energy Filler, equipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:52.43,Default,283,0000,0000,0000,,Fully stable and suppressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:54.20,Default,284,0000,0000,0000,,Energy Filler humidity level is accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:54.83,Default,285,0000,0000,0000,,Voltage begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:56.44,Default,286,0000,0000,0000,,30 seconds to maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:57.75,Default,287,0000,0000,0000,,Core Binding...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:14:59.96,Default,288,0000,0000,0000,,Devicer set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:01.79,Default,289,0000,0000,0000,,Devicer's 301.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:03.01,Default,290,0000,0000,0000,,Entry confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:05.63,Default,291,0000,0000,0000,,Location report input complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:08.50,Default,292,0000,0000,0000,,Interface self-support confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.43,Default,293,0000,0000,0000,,Yggdrasil control confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:11.91,Default,295,0000,0000,0000,,Rejection response is minimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:13.62,Default,296,0000,0000,0000,,Devicer stress response is minimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:15.33,Default,297,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is within the tolerance level.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.48,Default,298,0000,0000,0000,,Up to now has been according to the data...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:18.85,Default,299,0000,0000,0000,,Status: all green.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:20.14,Default,300,0000,0000,0000,,Back up, all back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:21.47,Default,301,0000,0000,0000,,Status acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:23.58,Default,302,0000,0000,0000,,Second reconfirm has finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.07,Default,303,0000,0000,0000,,Lancelot. ME-Boost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.97,Default,304,0000,0000,0000,,Lancelot, depart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:44.82,Default,305,0000,0000,0000,,Hahaha! Full throttle from the start, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.67,Default,306,0000,0000,0000,,This is greater than the manual!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:49.52,Default,307,0000,0000,0000,,With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:52.08,Default,308,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:53.75,Default,309,0000,0000,0000,,For a Sutherland...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:16:00.27,Default,310,0000,0000,0000,,A little bit more and I can destroy the inspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.56,Default,311,0000,0000,0000,,This is B-group!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.65,Default,312,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:04.08,Default,313,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Is it backup?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.90,Default,314,0000,0000,0000,,Real battle is different I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:07.04,Default,315,0000,0000,0000,,What's the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:10.42,Default,316,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone escaped but four troops were instantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:11.46,Default,317,0000,0000,0000,,Number of enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:12.36,Default,318,0000,0000,0000,,One troop, just one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.30,Default,319,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a new model?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:16.01,Default,320,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen that type bef... aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:17.99,Default,321,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:27.85,Default,322,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:32.32,Default,323,0000,0000,0000,,What? It can block bullets?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:33.82,Default,324,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:35.27,Default,325,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida! Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.72,Default,326,0000,0000,0000,,These terrorists are so useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:40.69,Default,327,0000,0000,0000,,It's only one troop and they can't handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:44.64,Default,328,0000,0000,0000,,Damnit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:50.77,Default,329,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.49,Default,330,0000,0000,0000,,With this Lancelot I can... do it all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:55.07,Default,331,0000,0000,0000,,N-4, N-5, hold it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.84,Default,332,0000,0000,0000,,When the high-speed squad gets there, surround it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:57.49,Default,333,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:05.42,Default,334,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stop this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:09.65,Default,335,0000,0000,0000,,Hey? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:12.11,Default,336,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:13.71,Default,337,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:18.30,Default,338,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it looks like I've incurred an unwanted debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:19.88,Default,339,0000,0000,0000,,However, with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:27.73,Default,340,0000,0000,0000,,P-1, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:31.66,Default,341,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is it really only one troop?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:36.59,Default,342,0000,0000,0000,,These numbers are above what we assumed it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:40.20,Default,343,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and he plans on going all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:47.79,Default,344,0000,0000,0000,,If I destroy all of the Knightmares, then the fighting will stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:51.17,Default,345,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, I need to save Lelouche and that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.67,Default,346,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the guy... the one who's messing with my plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:07.99,Default,348,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:11.51,Default,349,0000,0000,0000,,A mere pilot like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:12.12,Default,350,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:19.03,Default,351,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. I need to eject here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:29.11,Default,352,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:29.96,Default,353,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get him back for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:35.66,Default,354,0000,0000,0000,,So this is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:45.76,Default,355,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I must learn that with humans, there is no perfect plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:58.23,Default,357,0000,0000,0000,,What is that monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:03.03,Default,358,0000,0000,0000,,That guy has no concern for how high the casualties rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:13.92,Default,359,0000,0000,0000,,Saving a person in the middle of a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:17.65,Default,360,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. If you want moral victories, I'll give them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:18.79,Default,361,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:24.44,Default,362,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? An act of mercy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:26.20,Default,363,0000,0000,0000,,It appears to be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.46,Default,364,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. He's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:34.44,Default,365,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.95,Default,366,0000,0000,0000,,You're tired aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:37.13,Default,367,0000,0000,0000,,Should we end it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:38.73,Default,368,0000,0000,0000,,I will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.06,0:19:40.01,Default,369,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:42.73,Default,370,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful of the operation time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:43.54,Default,371,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:46.69,Default,372,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh. He's the perfect part.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:48.75,Default,373,0000,0000,0000,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:49.51,Default,374,0000,0000,0000,,Where is your ID?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:52.28,Default,375,0000,0000,0000,,This is Prince Clovis' apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:54.22,Default,376,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, a guard huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:56.34,Default,377,0000,0000,0000,,You've become quite spread out, as I planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.04,Default,378,0000,0000,0000,,Plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:59.70,Default,379,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I want you to let me pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:02.13,Default,380,0000,0000,0000,,I see. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:07.68,Default,381,0000,0000,0000,,Kallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:11.08,Default,382,0000,0000,0000,,This happened because you people decided to turn against Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:12.09,Default,383,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:13.64,Default,384,0000,0000,0000,,You cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:16.07,Default,385,0000,0000,0000,,How many people do you think have died?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:16.66,Default,386,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:19.28,Default,387,0000,0000,0000,,We've also had a lot of our people killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:20.71,Default,388,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:22.12,Default,389,0000,0000,0000,,Ougi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:23.24,Default,390,0000,0000,0000,,What about that person who was talking to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:24.53,Default,391,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:27.17,Default,392,0000,0000,0000,,He won't answer the calls either so... He might have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:32.97,Default,393,0000,0000,0000,,See, I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:36.78,Default,394,0000,0000,0000,,We would've been better off to use the poison gas than ending up listening to some guy we don't even know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:37.78,Default,395,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:39.03,Default,396,0000,0000,0000,,Nagata, that idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:45.13,Default,397,0000,0000,0000,,So this was where you 11's have been hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:46.80,Default,398,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:50.42,Default,399,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.44,Default,400,0000,0000,0000,,To all troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:54.48,Default,401,0000,0000,0000,,Cease fire immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:56.56,Default,402,0000,0000,0000,,Cease fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:21:02.56,Default,403,0000,0000,0000,,As Area 11's governor, I command you in the name of the 3rd, Prince Clovis la Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:05.36,Default,404,0000,0000,0000,,All troops, cease fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:08.84,Default,405,0000,0000,0000,,Cease all structural destruction activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:12.97,Default,406,0000,0000,0000,,Aid the injured ones regardless of whether they are Britannian citizens or 11's.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:16.05,Default,407,0000,0000,0000,,I command you in the name of Clovis la Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.34,Default,408,0000,0000,0000,,Cease fire immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:20.44,Default,409,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow anymore conflict!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:23.48,Default,410,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:25.44,Default,411,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:26.71,Default,412,0000,0000,0000,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:28.15,Default,413,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I sing a song for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:30.63,Default,414,0000,0000,0000,,Or be your opponent in chess?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:32.14,Default,415,0000,0000,0000,,It brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:37.82,Default,416,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:39.64,Default,417,0000,0000,0000,,We always would play chess together,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:42.17,Default,418,0000,0000,0000,,even though I always won.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:42.94,Default,419,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:45.99,Default,420,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? At Alius' imperial Villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.24,Default,421,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:48.84,Default,421,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:51.57,Default,422,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:55.84,Default,423,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Empress Mariann is the eldest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:57.83,Default,424,0000,0000,0000,,I am the 17th successor, the second in line to throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:00.27,Default,425,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouche vie Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:03.18,Default,426,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouche? But you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.18,0:22:05.26,Default,427,0000,0000,0000,,"...supposed to be dead?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:12.25,Default,428,0000,0000,0000,,I have returned, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:15.59,Default,429,0000,0000,0000,,In order to change everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.48,0:23:52.88,Preview,429,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was impossible for a mere student to do something about the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.43,0:23:55.10,Preview,429,0000,0000,0000,,It's not realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.10,0:23:57.03,Preview,429,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to think very hard to realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.37,0:24:00.50,Preview,429,0000,0000,0000,,However, if the ability is in my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:04.43,Preview,429,0000,0000,0000,,Probably, the choice that I should take is...
